quran[9{c,v,t}:
30,42,keh do ke malik mein chalo phiro aur dekho ke jo log ( tum se ) pehlay hue hain un ka kaisa injaam howa hai. un mein ziyada tar mushriq hi they
30,43,to is roz se pehlay jo khuda ki taraf se aakar rahay ga aur ruk nahi sakay ga deen ( ke raste ) par seedha munh kiye chalay chalo is roz ( sab ) log munhtashir ho jaien ge
30,44,jis shakhs ne kufarkiya to is ke kufar ka zarrar usi ko hai aur jis ne naik amal kiye to aisay log apne hi liye aaraam gaah durust karte hain
30,45,jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay unn ko khuda apne fazl se badla day ga. bay shak woh kafiroon ko dost nahi rakhta
30,46,aur usi ki nshanyon mein se hai ke hawaon ko bhejta hai ke khushkhabri deti hain taakay tum ko apni rehmat ke mazay chakha-ay aur taakay is ke hukum se kashtiyan chalein aur taakay is ke fazl se ( rozi ) talab karo ajab nahi ke tum shukar karo
30,47,aur hum ne tum se pehlay bhi paighambar un ki qoum ki taraf beje to woh unn ke paas nishanain le kar aeye so jo log nafarmani karte they hum ne unn se badla le kar chorra aur mominoun ki madad hum par lazim thi
30,48,khuda hi to hai jo hawaon ko chalata hai to woh baadal ko abharti hain. phir khuda is ko jis terhan chahta hai aasman mein phela deta aur teh-ba-teh kar deta hai phir tum dekhte ho ke is ke beech mein semeinhہ niklny lagta hai phir jab woh apne bundon mein se jin par chahta hai ussay barsa deta hai to woh khush ho jatay hain
30,49,aur beshtar to wohmeinhہ ke aُtrne se pehlay na umeed ho rahay they
30,50,to ( ae dekhnay walay ) khuda ki rehmat ki nshanyon ki taraf dekh ke woh kis terhan zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. bay shak woh mardon ko zindah karne wala hai. aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
